      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The Switch of course is a tailor-made console for indie games due to its scope and functionality, and I’m pleased to report that "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Turnip Boy Commits Tax Evasion "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "fits the Switch aesthetic perfectly; colourful, fun(ny) and accessible."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "It plays out like a 2D action-RPG, but in the most basic sense of the term. There’s an abundance of item collecting/trading and small dungeon type areas to explore as you scurry around the game world in a top-down perspective. There’s also combat involved, although the combat merely feels like a side quest that gets in the way of the relentless collecting/trading. "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
