          0,
          "Personally I like collecting/trading items and its rewarding to work out what to give to whom based on the dialogue clues that you get from the various vegetable NPCs, but if you find all that kind of business quite tiresome then probably best to avoid "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Turnip Boy Commits Tax Evasion "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "altogether. There also isn’t much in the way of skilling or levelling up which is why I stressed earlier that the term ‘RPG’ is very generous, however you are able to collect items and weapons along the way that slightly improve Turnip Boy’s combat abilities."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "h3",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Story / Personality"
        ]
